Introduction

Riracha Phondechaphiphat, known under her stage name Chiquita, is a Thai singer and dancer under YG Entertainment. She is best known as the maknae and one of the lead vocalists and lead dancers of the girl group BABYMONSTER. She made her official debut on November 27, 2023 with the group's digital single "Batter Up".
